Package net.philsprojects.stat

Class Summary
StatArchive An archive contains a fixed number of points.
StatDatabase A database of round robin archives which hold the summary of a statistic over time.
StatEvent A StatisticEvent is triggered when a statistic (float) is added to a StatisticDatabase.
StatFormat The format of a database and its archives.
StatGroup A StatGroup represents a directory in the filesystem where its databases and child groups are stored.
StatPoint A single statistical point in an archive.
StatService The service responsible for handling statistic events.
 

Enum Summary
StatTarget Specifies the scope to which to perform an operation on a group.
 

Exception Summary
StatFormatException A problem occurred parsing an existing Store with a given StatFormat.
